{"id":21,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":21,"title":"Matthew 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus teaches about marriage and divorce—Eternal life is for those who keep the commandments—The Twelve Apostles will judge the house of Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.1","order":"03.03.019.2475"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass,",["i","that"],"when Jesus had finished these sayings, he departed from Galilee, and came into the coasts of Judæa beyond Jordan;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.2","order":"03.03.019.2476"},["b","2"],"And great multitudes followed him; and he healed them there."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.3","order":"03.03.019.2477"},["b","3"],"¶The Pharisees also came unto him, tempting him, and saying unto him, Is it lawful for a man to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"put away"],"his wife for every cause?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.4","order":"03.03.019.2478"},["b","4"],"And he answered and said unto them, Have ye not read, that he which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"made"],["i","them"],"at the beginning made them male and female,"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.5","order":"03.03.019.2479"},["b","5"],"And said, For this cause shall a man leave father and mother, and shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cleave"],"to his wife: and they twain shall be one flesh?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.6","order":"03.03.019.2480"},["b","6"],"Wherefore they are no more twain, but one flesh. What therefore God hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"joined"],"together, let not man",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"put asunder"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.7","order":"03.03.019.2481"},["b","7"],"They say unto him, Why did Moses then command to give a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"writing"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"divorcement"],", and to put her away?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.8","order":"03.03.019.2482"},["b","8"],"He saith unto them, Moses because of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"hardness"],"of your hearts suffered you to put away your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"wives"],": but from the beginning it was not so."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.9","order":"03.03.019.2483"},["b","9"],"And I say unto you, Whosoever shall put away his wife, except",["i","it be"],"for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"fornication"],", and shall marry another, committeth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"adultery"],": and whoso marrieth her which is put away doth commit adultery."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.10","order":"03.03.019.2484"},["b","10"],"¶His disciples say unto him, If the case of the man be so with",["i","his"],"wife, it is not good to marry."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.11","order":"03.03.019.2485"},["b","11"],"But he said unto them, All",["i","men"],"cannot receive this saying, save",["i","they"],"to whom it is given."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.12","order":"03.03.019.2486"},["b","12"],"For there are some eunuchs, which were so born from",["i","their"],"mother’s womb: and there are some eunuchs, which were made eunuchs of men: and there be eunuchs, which have made themselves eunuchs for the kingdom of heaven’s sake. He that is able to receive",["i","it,"],"let him receive",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.13","order":"03.03.019.2487"},["b","13"],"¶Then were there brought unto him little children, that he should put",["i","his"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"hands"],"on them, and pray: and the disciples rebuked",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"them"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.14","order":"03.03.019.2488"},["b","14"],"But Jesus said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Suffer"],"little",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"children"],", and forbid them not, to come unto me: for of such is the kingdom of heaven."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.15","order":"03.03.019.2489"},["b","15"],"And he laid",["i","his"],"hands on them, and departed thence."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.16","order":"03.03.019.2490"},["b","16"],"¶And, behold, one came and said unto him, Good Master, what good thing shall I do, that I may have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"eternal life"],"?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.17","order":"03.03.019.2491"},["b","17"],"And he said unto him, Why callest thou me good?",["i","there is"],"none",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"good"],"but one,",["i","that is,"],"God: but if thou wilt enter into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"life"],", keep the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"commandments"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.18","order":"03.03.019.2492"},["b","18"],"He saith unto him, Which? Jesus said, Thou shalt do no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"murder"],", Thou shalt not commit",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"adultery"],", Thou shalt not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"steal"],", Thou shalt not bear",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"false witness"],","],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.19","order":"03.03.019.2493"},["b","19"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Honour"],"thy father and",["i","thy"],"mother: and, Thou shalt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"love"],"thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"neighbour"],"as thyself."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.20","order":"03.03.019.2494"},["b","20"],"The young man saith unto him, All these things have I kept from my youth up: what lack I yet?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.21","order":"03.03.019.2495"},["b","21"],"Jesus said unto him, If thou wilt be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"perfect"],", go",["i","and"],"sell that thou hast, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"give"],"to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"poor"],", and thou shalt have",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_21d"},"treasure"],"in heaven: and come",["i","and"],["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_21e"},"follow"],"me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.22","order":"03.03.019.2496"},["b","22"],"But when the young man heard that saying, he went away sorrowful: for he had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"great"],"possessions."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.23","order":"03.03.019.2497"},["b","23"],"¶Then said Jesus unto his disciples, Verily I say unto you, That a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"rich"],"man shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"hardly"],"enter into the kingdom of heaven."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.24","order":"03.03.019.2498"},["b","24"],"And again I say unto you, It is easier for a camel to go through the eye of a needle, than for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"rich"],"man to enter into the kingdom of God."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.25","order":"03.03.019.2499"},["b","25"],"When his disciples heard",["i","it,"],"they were exceedingly amazed, saying, Who then can be saved?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.26","order":"03.03.019.2500"},["b","26"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"But"],"Jesus beheld",["i","them,"],"and said unto them, With men this is impossible; but with God all things are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"possible"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.27","order":"03.03.019.2501"},["b","27"],"¶Then answered Peter and said unto him, Behold, we have forsaken all, and followed thee; what shall we have therefore?"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.28","order":"03.03.019.2502"},["b","28"],"And Jesus said unto them, Verily I say unto you, That ye which have followed me, in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"regeneration"],"when the Son of man shall sit in the throne of his glory, ye also shall sit upon twelve thrones,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"judging"],"the twelve tribes of Israel."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.29","order":"03.03.019.2503"},["b","29"],"And every one that hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"forsaken"],"houses, or brethren, or sisters, or father, or mother, or wife, or children, or lands, for my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"name’s"],"sake, shall receive an hundredfold, and shall inherit",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"everlasting life"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.30","order":"03.03.019.2504"},["b","30"],"But many",["i","that are"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"first"],"shall be last; and the last",["i","shall be"],"first."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.3a","order":"03.03.019.2505"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"divorce."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.4a","order":"03.03.019.2507"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-physical-creation-of"},"TG Man, Physical Creation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.5a","order":"03.03.019.2509"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"TG Family, Love within"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-celestial"},"Marriage, Celestial"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.6a","order":"03.03.019.2511"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-marry"},"TG Marriage, Marry"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.6b","order":"03.03.019.2513"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"divide, separate."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.7a","order":"03.03.019.2515"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"certificate of divorce."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.7b","order":"03.03.019.2517"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/divorce"},"TG Divorce"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.8a","order":"03.03.019.2519"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.8b","order":"03.03.019.2521"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-eternal"},"TG Family, Eternal"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.9a","order":"03.03.019.2523"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fornication"},"TG Fornication"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.9b","order":"03.03.019.2525"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"TG Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.13a","order":"03.03.019.2527"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"TG Hands, Laying on of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.13b","order":"03.03.019.2529"},["b","13b"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 19:13 … them,",["i","saying, There is no need, for Jesus hath said, Such shall be saved."]],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.14a","order":"03.03.019.2531"},["b","14a"],["span.small","GR"],"Allow, Permit."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.14b","order":"03.03.019.2533"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/137.10"},"D&C 137:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/children"},"TG Children"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-of-little-children"},"Salvation of Little Children"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.16a","order":"03.03.019.2535"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eternity"},"TG Eternity"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.17a","order":"03.03.019.2537"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-perfection-of"},"TG God, Perfection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.17b","order":"03.03.019.2539"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/4.22"},"Prov. 4:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.17c","order":"03.03.019.2541"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.31"},"1 Ne. 22:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.18a","order":"03.03.019.2543"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-shedding-of"},"TG Blood, Shedding of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/murder"},"Murder"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.18b","order":"03.03.019.2545"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.18c","order":"03.03.019.2547"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stealing"},"TG Stealing"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.18d","order":"03.03.019.2549"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/25.18"},"Prov. 25:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.19a","order":"03.03.019.2551"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-duties-of"},"TG Family, Children, Duties of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"Honoring Father and Mother"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.19b","order":"03.03.019.2553"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.19c","order":"03.03.019.2555"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fellowshipping"},"TG Fellowshipping"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/neighbor"},"Neighbor"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.21a","order":"03.03.019.2557"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.21b","order":"03.03.019.2559"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/almsgiving"},"TG Almsgiving"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.21c","order":"03.03.019.2561"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],"."],["div",{"id":"21d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.21d","order":"03.03.019.2563"},["b","21d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"21e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.21e","order":"03.03.019.2565"},["b","21e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/22.15"},"Alma 22:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.22a","order":"03.03.019.2567"},["b","22a"],["span.small","GR"],"many."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.23a","order":"03.03.019.2569"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.30"},"2 Ne. 9:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.19.16-19"},"Jacob 2:19 (16–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.7.5-7"},"D&C 6:7 (5–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.23b","order":"03.03.019.2571"},["b","23b"],["span.small","GR"],"with difficulty."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.24a","order":"03.03.019.2573"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/18.11"},"Prov. 18:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.26a","order":"03.03.019.2575"},["b","26a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 19:26 But Jesus beheld",["i","their thoughts,"],"and said unto them, With men this is impossible; but",["i","if they will forsake all things for my sake,"],"with God",["i","whatsoever things I speak"],"are possible."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.26b","order":"03.03.019.2577"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/42.2"},"Job 42:2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.28a","order":"03.03.019.2579"},["b","28a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 19:28 …",["i","resurrection"],"…"],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.28b","order":"03.03.019.2581"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/3.18.18-20"},"Morm. 3:18 (18–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.12"},"D&C 29:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostles"},"TG Apostles"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment-the-last"},"Judgment, the Last"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.29a","order":"03.03.019.2583"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.36"},"D&C 19:36"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"TG Self-Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.29b","order":"03.03.019.2585"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"29c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.29c","order":"03.03.019.2587"},["b","29c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/exaltation"},"TG Exaltation"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.30a","order":"03.03.019.2589"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.30"},"D&C 29:30"],"."]]}
